I, zoey, of The United Kingdom, a British Citizen under section 37(1) of the British Nationality Act of 1981

DO DECLARE THAT:

I ABSOLUTELY have renounced, relinquished and abandoned the use of any former name, and assume and determine to take, use and be known, exclusively, by only the name of zoey;

I AUTHORISE AND REQUEST all creatures at all times, to refer to me and address me as and by my name of zoey.

This has been publicly broadcast as being the case since May 1st 2016, took effect immediately, and reading this document imparts the knowledge on your behalf.
